{"tid":2141483,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"南韓成為中國首個放寬簽證限制既特定國家","createTime":"2020-08-05T17:03:56.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-05T19:40:48.000Z","uid":75656,"like":1,"dislike":18,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"c195a45d0391375d03c420d4d1ae89fc501c1d87","tid":2141483,"uid":75656,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T17:03:56.000Z","msg":"韓聯社引述北京消息人士透露，中國政府將從明日起受理出於留學、就業目的，或持有效居留證南韓公民的簽證申請。<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，這是新冠疫情在中國爆發以來，中方首次針對特定國家放寬簽證限制。中方自3月底起暫時禁止持有效簽證和居留證的外國人入境。中國駐韓大使館和領事館從明日起開始受理簽證申請，入境者必須提交乘機前5天內的核酸檢測陰性證明。<br />\n<br />\n分析認為，在中韓兩國有效管控疫情的情況下，為了恢復雙邊經濟交流，以及促成中國國家主席習近平年內訪韓，放寬入境管制不可避免。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2541753/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E5%8F%97%E7%90%86%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%B5%B4%E8%8F%AF%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fcurrent%2Farticle%2F2541753%2F%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E5%259C%258B%25E6%2593%259A%25E5%25A0%25B1%25E6%2598%258E%25E8%25B5%25B7%25E5%258F%2597%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%258D%2597%25E9%259F%2593%25E5%25BF%2585%25E8%25A6%2581%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E8%25B5%25B4%25E8%258F%25AF%25E7%25B0%25BD%25E8%25AD%2589&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2Fz11NNBcSSu27FcfjCvRQ4I%3D&h=d3f2185d\" target=\"_blank\">https://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/current/article/2541753/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9C%8B%E6%93%9A%E5%A0%B1%E6%98%8E%E8%B5%B7%E5%8F%97%E7%90%86%E5%8D%97%E9%9F%93%E5%BF%85%E8%A6%81%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E8%B5%B4%E8%8F%AF%E7%B0%BD%E8%AD%89</a>"},{"pid":"5a0f895634fa912cb1e81e90ac74586aadeba178","tid":2141483,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T17:29:03.000Z","msg":"奶啊奶"},{"pid":"a55e9823440b440f3b0e90b366c313264e1948b1","tid":2141483,"uid":31946,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a0f895634fa912cb1e81e90ac74586aadeba178","tid":2141483,"uid":21545,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08